---
title: Bulgogi Lime Pork Tenderloin with a Roasted Sweet Potato & Bell Pepper Jumble
description: Raise your hand if the biggest question of your week is always, “What the heck am I eating for dinner?!” While we can’t actually see you, we’re right there with you. FYI, the answer to that question is pretty delicious. We’re serving up succulent pork tenderloin with a side of roasted sweet potatoes, bell pepper, and poblano all tossed in garlicky lime butter. To finish things off, the pork is drizzled with a ridiculously delicious soy-spiked pan sauce. Talk about a dream come true!
